  "2330360": {
    "name": "Pixel Art Academy: Learn Mode",
    "steam_appid": 2330360,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "Pixel Art Academy is an educational game for learning how to draw. In Learn Mode, you jump straight into the game's interactive tutorials for the fastest way of becoming a pixel artist. After you learn the rules behind pixel art lines, test your skills by drawing fan art and unleash your creativity with designing and illustrating your own pinball machine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/68cb6539a8394ed9cb7c4904f1b68a4e.poster.avif?t=1723634852\" width=616 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/68cb6539a8394ed9cb7c4904f1b68a4e.webm?t=1723634852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/68cb6539a8394ed9cb7c4904f1b68a4e.mp4?t=1723634852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Please note that during Early Access the game does not cover all areas of art yet!</i><br><br>The game's content is organized around the 7 elements of art: line, shape, form, space, value, color, and texture. The current version only covers lines with about 2–3 hours of gameplay for a minimal playthrough (more if you complete all the challenges and put extra effort into game projects). The other 6 elements are planned to be developed during Early Access.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An immersive user interface with a cozy, relaxing atmosphere.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/a8c802fdebccc402c6fb167d51dec989.poster.avif?t=1723634852\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/a8c802fdebccc402c6fb167d51dec989.webm?t=1723634852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/a8c802fdebccc402c6fb167d51dec989.mp4?t=1723634852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Carefully designed interactive tutorials teach how to use drawing tools, followed by intermediate lessons covering pixel art fundamentals with a focus on line art and jaggies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/d41892b0be9080db632f2da33f647a40.poster.avif?t=1723634852\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/d41892b0be9080db632f2da33f647a40.webm?t=1723634852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/d41892b0be9080db632f2da33f647a40.mp4?t=1723634852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Put theory into practice with drawing challenges where you copy other indie game sprites or draw fan art from reference.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/7682382c2fcd7e7f5449c30db5fc30a1.poster.avif?t=1723634852\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/7682382c2fcd7e7f5449c30db5fc30a1.webm?t=1723634852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/7682382c2fcd7e7f5449c30db5fc30a1.mp4?t=1723634852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Design video game sprites as you customize the game Snake and create your very own pinball machine. Of course, you get to play the games as well!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/81889964b0978664cc124164429a2199.poster.avif?t=1723634852\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/81889964b0978664cc124164429a2199.webm?t=1723634852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/81889964b0978664cc124164429a2199.mp4?t=1723634852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Get in the groove with more than 6 hours of background music to accompany your drawing sessions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/ca4022af5ab84d4adab9e7fb4f06b621.poster.avif?t=1723634852\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/ca4022af5ab84d4adab9e7fb4f06b621.webm?t=1723634852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/ca4022af5ab84d4adab9e7fb4f06b621.mp4?t=1723634852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Future development</h2>Please keep in mind that the game is designed, drawn, and coded by a single person—me! I also have to run the business side of things, do marketing, and organize collaborations with other artists, all of which take time. Expect slow, but steady progress. I have been working on the bigger Pixel Art Academy universe for 9 years now and I don't intend to stop any time soon.<br><br>I also keep a completely transparent development process. Visit my YouTube channel for frequent devlogs or catch me anywhere on the internet to chat about current progress.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/195e6cc8e13c4c079f2503d7f7b1c768.poster.avif?t=1723634852\" width=616 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/195e6cc8e13c4c079f2503d7f7b1c768.webm?t=1723634852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330360/extras/195e6cc8e13c4c079f2503d7f7b1c768.mp4?t=1723634852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
